data.description: Here is a charming  2 bed 1 bath bungalow in a quiet Morningside neighborhood. It sits on a corner lot with a nice deck, patio and a huge 3-car garage that can be used as a mechanics shop or for extra storage and it is also heated!  Many updates have been done. It is now vacant! Don't miss this opportunity, it won't last long!
